modShortDescription: Adding canned food crafting unlocked at Master Chef level 5. Finally a use for cans and a nice compliment to the Working Microwave mod.
modDescription:
Adding canned [food](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-food/) crafting unlocked at Master Chef level 5\. Finally a use for cans and a nice compliment to the [Working Microwave](https://7daystodiemods.com/working-microwaves/) mod. The recipes are janky because we do not have pears or peas or different meat and fish but hey we can hold 5000 concrete blocks in our bag so… lol

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/JaxTeller718/A20ModletsJax/tree/main/JaxTeller718-CannedFood)**

If you appreciate JaxTeller718’s work and you want to show support, use this [donate link](https://www.paypal.me/FrankCirabisiJr).
